{\*\bkmkstart id7c6acdf0_ad1c_439f_ab10_679e6c1f0c}\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li1588\ri0\fi-794\tqc\tx1191\tx1588\tab (a)\tab for the medical 
