\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\keepn\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 correctional order
} means an order under a law of this State or any other State for dealing with 
youths who commit offences, being an order\u8212 ?\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li1588\ri0\fi-794\tqc\tx1191\tx1588\tab (a)\tab for the detention 
