\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li1588\ri0\fi-794\tqc\tx1191\tx1588\tab (d)\tab placing such 
a youth on probation or parole or under any form of supervision;\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 correctional system
}, in relation to a State, means the system of law, judicial and administrative 
authorities, correctional and other institutions under which youths who commit 
offences are dealt with in that State;\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 corresponding law
} means a law of another State declared by regulation to be a law corresponding 
