\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 escort
} means a person in whose custody a young offender is placed for the purpose 
of bringing the young offender into the State, or taking the young offender 
out of the State, pursuant to arrangements made under this Division;\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 State
} includes the Australian Capital Territory and the Northern Territory;\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\keepn\widctlpar\li794\ri0\fi0
{\plain\f0\fs23\b\i\expnd0\kerning0\cf0 young offender
} means a person\u8212 ?\par
\pard\plain\f0\fs23\expnd0\kerning0\cf0\sb120\sa0
\sl240\slmult1\ql\keep\widctlpar\li1588\ri0\fi-794\tqc\tx1191\tx1588\tab (a)\tab who has been 
